  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Quality of Life</measure>
    <time_frame>Six months</time_frame>
    <description>Change in EuroQol five dimension (EQ-5D) score. The descriptive system comprises 5 dimensions (mobili-ty, self care, usual activities, pain/discomfort, anxiety/depression). However, each dimension has 5 levels: no problems, slight problems, moderate problems, severe problems, and extreme problems. The answers given to EQ-5D permit to find 243 unique health states or can be converted into EQ-5D index an utility scores anchored at 0 for death and 1 for perfect health.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
